                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "While a secondary or melee weapon is equipped, Catalyzer Link's buff icon still triggers when an ability is casted, this appears to be a lingering effect to reap the benefits of the mod when you switch to your primary, as status chance does not seem to increase for secondary and melee weapons."
